<big>Overview:</big>
</span>
<br>
<br>
Entity 484 – known among superstitious wanderers as “The Grim Reaper’s Curse”, or simply as “the Reaper” – is a parasitic entity that presents itself in various shapes and forms depending on its victim. The creature itself is a hyperintelligent field of energy, one that can detect life and suitable targets around it with uncomfor<span style="font-family: f-fatamor">table precision. Wh</span>en a host drifts into its vicinity, the field tightens, constantly measuring the wanderer’s state. Only then does a manifestation take shape, usually aligning itself with whatever the wanderer is most likely to trust. Although it can present itself at any time, the Reaper always arrives when its sufferer plans to depart.<br><br>
If a victim finds 484’s embodim<span style='font-family: f-fatamor">ent, it will rarely be in a form</span> they expect. The entity deliberately chooses configurations of itself that appear harmless, convenient, or even comforting. In colder levels, it will present itself as a source of heat, such as a fireplace or a winter coat. In other environments, it <span style='font-family: f-fatamor'>hides in whatever cou</span>ld attract attention. The entity prefers to blend in, to look and feel ordinary, even when it is clear it isn’t.<br><br> 
Once a body has been connected to a <span style='font-family: f-fatamor'>stronghold, their cellular energy will begin to drain almost immediately, dissipating into the</span> surrounding air.  During this entire step, the victim rarely realizes what is happening, until it is too late. Slowly, the entity will eat away at life, <span style='font-family: f-fatamor'>deteriorating its user and removing their memories until nothing is left. And when the body can no longer fuel the process, the f</span>inal part begins.<br><br>
After the wanderer’s soul has been chained to a manifestation, it is forced to remain alive by the continual feeding of nearby energy. This trapped consciousness is <span style='font-family: f-fatamor'>unallowed to sleep or stay awake, holding a state that is neither living or dead. The energy created through this exchange fuels Entity 484’s existence, allowing it to maintain its manifestations and seek out future hosts. Any attempt to escape its grasp is pointless, not because</span> it constrains the wanderer physically, but because it offers something no living thing can refuse. It allows its subject to gain immortality, even in a life of torture. And, once someone holds that power in their hand, they will never let it go.<br><br>
<span style='font-family: f-fatamor'>Eternal life, stuck in servitude.
<br>Eternal life, </span>carried<span style='font-family: f-fatamor'> out in unending pain.
<br>Eternal</span> life,<span style='font-family: f-fatamor'> granted with no mercy.</span>
<br><br><div style='font-family: f-fatamor'>This is the price of living forever.


